{"tid":1156331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾經帶領網絡惡搞/創作文化，於4chan，eBaum同YouTube之前已經存在嘅YTMND網站正式死亡","createTime":"2019-05-15T14:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T15:14:03.000Z","uid":131691,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"29db93e070e000382b612a79382a524f33f2e0fe","tid":1156331,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rkFgsL7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrkFgsL7.gif&h=d23622c2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n年輕一輩可能未聽過咩係YTMND (You The Man Now Dog)，佢係一個2001年創立，曾經紅極一時嘅網站/網上社區。該網站嘅網民會創作一啲得一個page嘅網頁，大部份都係一個簡單gif加音樂，係咁loop，每一個呢啲網頁叫一個fad。有啲純粹搞笑，有啲好有趣，有啲remix人哋fad，有啲諷刺時弊，有啲完全癡線。唔少2001-2006嘅網絡文化都係咁樣喺YTMND呢個網絡社區爆咗出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n當年最出名嘅，莫過於What is love呢個fad，好彩Internet Archive存檔咗：<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190212212742/http://ckjcwf.ytmnd.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20190212212742%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fckjcwf.ytmnd.com%2F&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2GsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=824e32fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20190212212742/http://ckjcwf.ytmnd.com/</a><br />\n其餘嘅，有啲喺YouTube記錄咗，有啲喺Internet Archive，有啲喺個人網站backup:<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150708132902/http://takemeoutflanders.ytmnd.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20150708132902%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Ftakemeoutflanders.ytmnd.com%2F&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2GsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=47af964c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20150708132902/http://takemeoutflanders.ytmnd.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150421053422/http://freecow.ytmnd.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20150421053422%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Ffreecow.ytmnd.com%2F&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2GsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=1720a4cf\" data-auto-link target=\